The [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Alien/Legends|alien]] [[Species/Legends|race]] '''Fraii Wys''' was thought to be extinct for a very extended period of [[Time/Legends|time]]. Then after nine thousand [[Standard year/Legends|years]], they reappeared in the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]] and flourished. It was an extraordinary case brought up when considering the truth behind the disappearance of the [[Qella]].<ref name="tt">''[[Tyrant's Test]]''</ref>

